window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The fae spend their entire lives searching for their true mate.<br> But me? I know who my mine is.<br> And I don't want him.<br> My name is Astrid. I'm a fae—a seer and a healer.<br> Not much scares me. But him?<br> That's the darkness I'm never going to let catch me.</p> <p><b><i>Forewarned</i></b><b> is book one in the new gripping, sexy romantic fantasy series by Chantal Fernando.</b></p>"; 
